article_title: Bill Maher Proves Americans Know Nothing About Obamacare (VIDEO)
article_text:
Wayne Brady

This July, Wayne Brady went on Aisha Tyler's podcast to discuss his disapproval of Bill Maher's description of President Obama as " Your Wayne Brady ," saying he would "Slap the sh*t" out of the comedian.
